    • remove

      boolean remove​(java.lang.String index)
      Removes the cell corresponding to the index. If such an index does not exist, returns false. On successful removal - returns true and keeps the index.
      Parameters:
      index - - index of the cell to be removed
      Returns:
      cell removal status

    • removeIndex

      boolean removeIndex​(java.lang.String index)
      Removes the index and associated data. If such an index does not exist, returns false. On successful removal - returns true.
      Parameters:
      index - - index to be removed
      Returns:
      index removal status

    • updateIndexes

      void updateIndexes​(java.util.ArrayList<java.lang.String> indexes)
      Update indexes. All data that is associated to other indexes than those in the input array is removed.
      Parameters:
      indexes - - new indexes

      Prints the items of the column.
